These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: tea, mirinda
The people have 2 different hobbies: traveling, singing
The people have 2 different jobs:  coach, project-manager
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: disaster, time-travel
There are 2 different nationalities: colombian, argentine
2 different pets are kept: cat, ferret
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, van
1. the person drinking tea is on the far right##1
2. the project-manager is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the van is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
4. the owner of the cat is the argentine##1
5. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person driving the van##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |
| Beverage      | mirinda     | tea       |
| Hobby         | traveling   | singing     |
| Job           | coach | project-manager   |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel   | disaster  |
| Nationality   | argentine | colombian |
| Pet           | cat      | ferret     |
| Transport     | van    | quad-bike   |

