.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, milk
The people have 2 different hobbies: card-games, rock-climbing
The people have 2 different jobs:  coach, mechanic
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, house
There are 2 different nationalities: american, turkish
2 different pets are kept: frog, goat
The people use 2 different means of transport: roller, train
1. the mechanic is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the owner of the goat is the person driving the train##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the fan of punk##1
4. the turkish is on the far right##1
5. the person drinking soy-milk is the owner of the frog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk    | milk |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing        | card-games  |
| Job           | coach | mechanic  |
| Music-Genre   | house            | punk    |
| Nationality   | american     | turkish   |
| Pet           | frog         | goat    |
| Transport     | roller           | train      |

